        {
            "title": "中國｜習近平重要文章指出要推動全民閱讀　建設學習型社會",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中國｜習近平重要文章指出要推動全民閱讀 建設學習型社會\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國｜習近平重要文章指出要推動全民閱讀 建設學習型社會</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">明天出版的《求是》雜誌，將發表中共中央總書記、國家主席、中央軍委主席習近平的重要文章。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文章題為《推動全民閱讀，建設書香社會》，指出閱讀是人類獲取知識、啟智增慧、培養道德的重要途徑，可以讓人得到思想啟發，樹立崇高理想，涵養浩然之氣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文章指出，要建設全民終身學習的學習型社會、學習型大國，促進人人皆學、處處能學、時時可學，促進人的全面發展。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文章提到，希望孩子養成閱讀習慣，快樂閱讀，健康成長，亦希望全社會都參與閱讀，形成愛讀書、讀好書、善讀書的濃厚氛圍。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%8C%87%E5%87%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80-%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E5%9E%8B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83-101215306.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 18:23:51",
